WEBVTT

00:12:58.901 --> 00:13:03.893
I remembered that in Utica, an hour away,

00:13:03.917 --> 00:13:07.686
there were refugees
from Southeast Asia and Africa,

00:13:07.710 --> 00:13:09.752
who were looking for a place to work.

00:13:11.518 --> 00:13:13.590
"They don't speak English,"
someone told me.

00:13:13.614 --> 00:13:16.284
I said, "I don't really, either.
Let's get translators."

00:13:16.308 --> 00:13:18.819
(Laughter)

00:13:19.327 --> 00:13:20.990
"They don't have transportation."

00:13:21.014 --> 00:13:23.616
I said, "Let's get buses,
it's not a rocket science."

00:13:24.506 --> 00:13:25.656
Today,

00:13:27.339 --> 00:13:30.196
in one of America's rural areas,